61 (c)(1) Members Commencing on October 1, 2026, members
62 of the board shall be appointed for terms of six years
63 commencing on July 1 March 1. in the years 1953, 1955, and
64 1957, and The terms of the members serving on the board on
65 October 1, 2026, shall end on the last day of February during
