72 (d) The Governor shall designate one of the members as
73 chair, and the chair shall preside at sessions of the board.
74 (e) Each member shall take the constitutional oath of
75 office and shall be subject to impeachment for any of the
76 causes specified in Section 173 of the Constitution; and the
